{"word":"G4859 - σύμφωνος - sýmphōnos - soom'-fo-nos - Consent","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σύμφωνος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">sýmphōnos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soom'-fo-nos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Consent</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"சம்மதித்த - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"harmonious, accordant, agreeing"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G5456 - φωνή - phōnḗ - fo-nay'/5456\">G5456</a>; <i>sounding together</i> (<i>alike</i>), that is, (figuratively) <i>accordant</i> (neuter as noun, <i>agreement</i>): - consent.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2019/2019\">G2019</a>, <a href=\"#/G4856/4856\">G4856</a>, <a href=\"#/G4857/4857\">G4857</a>, <a href=\"#/G4858/4858\">G4858</a>, <a href=\"#/G4859/4859\">G4859</a>, <a href=\"#/G5455/5455\">G5455</a>, <a href=\"#/G5456/5456\">G5456</a>"}]}